		<title>Following a China Regulator&#8217;s Assurance on New Regulations, Tencent and NetEase Shares Rise</title>
		<link>https://thecioworld.com/following-a-china-regulators-assurance-on-new-regulations-tencent-and-netease-shares-rise/</link>
					<comments>https://thecioworld.com/following-a-china-regulators-assurance-on-new-regulations-tencent-and-netease-shares-rise/#respond</comments>
		
